| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0696 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c1d55cea-6fd0-5f74-9ea1-49b509a0dcad"
